            </output_collection>
        </test>
    </tests>
    <help><![CDATA[
**What it does**

This tool runs the ``samtools stats`` command.

The results of samtools stats can be visualized with MultiQC (for this the default of a single output file needs to be selected).
    ]]></help>
    <expand macro="citations"/>
</tool>

